request.description:
## Check email: negative cases

| Key| Description |
| ------ | ----------- |
| Email   | Enter register email of teacher |
| Validation| Unique |
| Format    |text@text.text |
| Max length    |255 |
| Required    |Not null |

## Case 1



+ Step 1: Enter email registered successfully
+ Step 2: Keep other valid value 
+ Step 3: click [Send] request

## Case 2: Enter invalid  email format
| Data| Description |
| ------ | ----------- |
| Data 1  | text@text. |
| Data 2| text@.text |
| Data 3    |@text.text |
| Data 4     |@text.|
| Data 5    |text.text |
| Data 6    |.text |
| Data 7    |text@ |

+ Step 1: Enter invalid email format( in table above)
+ Step 2: Keep other valid value 
+ Step 3: click [Send] request

-> Expect: Error 400: bad request: invalid email address
## Case 3: Email does not match max length
| Data| Description |
| ------ | ----------- |
| Data 1  | length = 256 |
| Data 2| length= null |

-> Expect: Error 400: bad request: invalid email address

## Description

| Key | Description |
| ------ | ----------- |
| Password   | Password of teacher register |
| format | at least 1 uppercase letter, 1 special character, 1 number   |
| Maxlength   | 8-16|
| Required   | Not null|

## Case 1: invalid format password

| Data | Description |
| ------ | ----------- |
| Data 1   | no number and no uppercase: h@ |
| Data 2 | no special character and no uppercase: h1   |
| Data 3   | no special character and no number: HoanG|

## steps:


1. Step 1: enter invalid format password( above data)
2. Step 2: Keep other valid value
3. Step 3: Click [Send] request 

=> Expect: 400 error: bad request, invalid password

## Case 2:  password does not match maxlength

| Data | Description |
| ------ | ----------- |
| Data 1   | length 7: H@34567 |
| Data 2 | length 17: H@34567899999999    |

## steps:

1. Step 1: enter password with length 7 or 17
2. Step 2: Keep other valid value
3. Step 3: Click [Send] request 

=> Expect: 400 error: bad request, invalid password

## Case 3:  Null password 

1. Step 1: Do not enter password
2. Step 2: Keep other valid value
3. Step 3: Click [Send] request

=> Expect: 400 error: bad request, password could not be blank
